room_title: Escape room "Sabotage!!" by Escape SBC in Shreveport
room_description:
Sabotage (verb) – to deliberately destroy, damage, or obstruct.

Sailors, your mission is simple.  There is a traitor among us and is wreaking havoc!  They have altered the vessel’s control systems and have armed the nuclear warheads aboard the USS Unite.  Can you power down the weapons system to reclaim the ship or will you be blasted into oblivion by the betrayer’s wretched plans??  SAVE OUR SOULS!!
